essdate=2019-10-23}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" |\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{flag|Romania}}\n| style=\"background:Gainsboro\" align=\"center\" |None<ref name=\"romania\" />\n| align=\"center\" |18<ref name=\"romania\" />\n| colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |18<ref name=\"romania\">{{cite web|url=http://www.euroavocatura.ro/legislatie/853/Legea_61_1991__republicata_2011_,_pentru_sanctionarea_faptelor_de_incalcare_a_unor_norme_de_convietuire_sociala,_a_ordinii_si_linistii_publice|title=Legea nr. 61/1991 (Actualizata 2008), pentru sanctionarea faptelor de incalcare a unor norme de convietuire sociala, a ordinii si linistii publice|last=|first=|date=June 2011|website=|language=Romanian|accessdate=2019-10-23}}</ref>\n| \n|-\n| colspan=\"2\" |{{flag|Russia}}\n| style=\"background:Gainsboro\" align=\"center\" |None\n|16<ref name=\":5\">{{Cite web|url=https://legalacts.ru/kodeks/KOAP-RF/|title=\"\u041a\u043e\u0434\u0435\u043a\u0441 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0439\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u043e\u0431 \u0430\u0434\u043c\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0432\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0448\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f\u0445\" \u043e\u0442 30.12.2001 N 195-\u0424\u0417 (\u0440\u0435\u0434. \u043e\u0442 02.08.2019) (\u0441 \u0438\u0437\u043c. \u0438 \u0434\u043e\u043f., \u0432\u0441\u0442\u0443\u043f. \u0432 \u0441\u0438\u043b\u0443 \u0441 01.09.2019)|last=|first=|date=|website=|access-date=2019-10-23}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" |18<ref>{{cite web|url=https://legalacts.ru/doc/171_FZ-o-gosudarstvennom-regulirovanii-proizvodstva-i-oborota-jetilovogo-spirta_-alkogolnoj-i-spirtosoderzhawej-produkcii/|title=\u0424\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u0437\u0430\u043a\u043e\u043d \u043e\u0442 22.11.1995 N 171-\u0424\u0417 (\u0440\u0435\u0434. \u043e\u0442 01.05.2019) \"\u041e \u0433\u043e\u0441\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0440\u0441\u0442\